OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will stay dry throughout the
OL,6,Fday on Friday with good lengthy bright
OL,7,For sunny spells. Winds will stay light
OL,8,Fand somewhat variable through the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FStaying dry with clear skies
OL,11,Fat first, but high cloud spreading in
OL,12,Ffrom the west later. Freshening south
OL,13,Fto southwest winds developing.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FIt will remain dry with some
OL,16,Fbright spells on Saturday, but
OL,17,Fsunshine quite hazy with high level
OL,18,Fcloud. Fresh to strong southerly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
