OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud punctured by bright spells on
OL,7,FSunday and Monday, staying mainly dry
OL,8,Fbut with the odd shower. Dry start
OL,9,FTuesday, windier and cloudier with
OL,10,Fsome rain later.
